      "role": "user",
      "content": "but putting in more effort just feels like running on a treadmill. i'm exerting so much energy just to stay in the same place of misery. what's the point of \"changing my approach\" if the result is always the same? it feels less like a pattern to fix and more like a trap i'm stuck in.",
